<%@ Page Title="About" Language="C#" MasterPageFile="~/Site.Master" AutoEventWireup="true" CodeBehind="About.aspx.cs" Inherits="FoodDeliveryApp.About" %>

<asp:Content ID="BodyContent" ContentPlaceHolderID="MainContent" runat="server">
    <main style="text-align:justify">
        <h3 id="title" class="mt-2"><%: Title %> - Food Delivery Website</h3>
        <p>Welcome to our Food Delivery Service, where we bring your favorite meals right to your doorstep with just a few clicks. We are committed to offering you a quick, easy, and convenient way to satisfy your hunger with a variety of delicious food options. Whether you're craving comfort food, healthy meals, or something exotic, we've got you covered.</p>
        <p>Our platform allows you to browse through a wide selection of local restaurants and food vendors, all in one place. Each restaurant offers its own unique menu, and you can explore a range of cuisines, including fast food, vegan, vegetarian, gourmet, and more. With high-quality images, detailed descriptions, and customer reviews, you can make an informed decision before placing your order</p>
        <h3>How It Works:</h3>
        <p><strong>1. Browse the Menu:</strong> Browse our curated food menu featuring a variety of delicious dishes. Filter options by cuisine, dietary preferences, and price range to find exactly what you're in the mood for.</p>
        <p><strong>2. Add to Cart:</strong> Once you’ve selected your meal, simply add it to your cart. You can adjust quantities, remove items, and review your selections before checking out.</p>
        <p><strong>3. Secure Checkout:</strong> After reviewing your cart, proceed to checkout where you can enter your delivery details, choose a secure payment method, and confirm your order.</p>
        <p><strong>4. Enjoy Your Meal: </strong> Sit back and relax as we bring your meal to you. Whether you're enjoying lunch at work, a cozy dinner at home, or a late-night snack, we’re here to serve you!</p>
        <p>We take pride in providing excellent customer service, offering timely deliveries, and ensuring your food arrives fresh and hot. Our goal is to make your dining experience as enjoyable as possible, all from the comfort of your home.</p>
    </main>
</asp:Content>
